job description:
Legal expert witness search firm looking to hire an Accounting & HR Manager for part-time or full-time work. The ideal candidate will have significant experience in all aspects of small-company accounting, including:
Billing and invoicing experience in Quickbooks Desktop
Experience in cash flow management
Providing oversight and managing all day-to-day aspects of the accounting department’s functions, including but not limited to: billing (which includes responding to consultant and client questions around billing and payment); payroll (including sales bonuses); accounts receivable; accounts payable; financial reporting including management reports; 1099 filings, general ledger and special reports as needed;
Maintaining fiscal files, documentation, and internal records as required;
Working with our external accounting consultants to ensure their work is accurate, timely and integrates with internal work;
Working with external tax accountants to close books and provide them with information to prepare our federal and multiple-state tax filings;
Assisting with the hiring and onboarding of new employees;
Helping to ensure compliance with relevant HR rules, regulations and statutes;
Working with our outside IT consultants to manage computer and email rights;
Assisting with the rollout and continued support of various technologies including (but not limited to) CRM; QuickBooks; phone; email; and file server.
Completing special projects as assigned;
Attending professional meetings as requested;
Significant experience with Quickbooks and MS Excel is required.
We are looking for someone who is detail-oriented, meticulous and thoughtful, who can work independently but can respond quickly to phone and email requests from outside clients and internal staff. We have been a virtual company for 20-years and expect to remain one after this crisis has passed. Our employees enjoy the flexible nature of our business even as they frequently interact with many of the friendly and talented people on our staff. Part-time desired (30 hours per week) but full-time is possible.
Job Type: Part-time
Pay: $32.00 - $50.00 per hour
Benefits:
Retirement plan
COVID-19 considerations:
We are a fully remote company.
Experience:
Accounting: 3 years (Required)
Microsoft Excel: 3 years (Required)
